### CST8917 - Smart PDF Analyzer
### REST Client test file (VS Code "REST Client" extension)
### Use the local or deployed base URL depending on what you're testing.

@localBaseUrl = http://localhost:7071/api
@azureBaseUrl = https://pdf-analyzer-vijay.azurewebsites.net/api

### Replace with a real document_id returned in your Azure Functions Core
### Tools terminal logs after uploading a PDF (see blob_trigger / orchestrator
### log lines: "Started orchestration instance_id=... for document_id=...")
@documentId = 80b7a218-2c0d-41d4-b9a4-2dc9fa126610

### 1. Get results - LOCAL (Azurite)
GET {{localBaseUrl}}/results/{{documentId}}
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get results - AZURE (deployed)
GET {{azureBaseUrl}}/results/{{documentId}}
Accept: application/json

### 3. Get results for a document_id that does not exist (should return 404)
GET {{localBaseUrl}}/results/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json
